{"tid":368410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"why my parents doesn't teach me chinese?","createTime":"2017-08-21T13:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T14:03:42.000Z","uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f17ba8178ae2820164c6df95db1befbc2ee8e2e","tid":368410,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"I am not white, I am local hongkong people<br />\nbut my parents never teach me chinese speaking or reading<br />\nCould anybody tell me why?<br />\nI feel bad when I cannot communicate with other people<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67579abc56c030fa883d93fb5d50c701db51a2e0","tid":368410,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"You are lazy"},{"pid":"7e4598ad9caf134fda08976c3ac9c42e999caf04","tid":368410,"uid":5489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"Can feel your Goodest English even in the topic"},{"pid":"3e9a5ae4604a90d53c8cde73e8b6743f7bd66a46","tid":368410,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b8ad7b0cfb737fc22937f0c3cb5c1d050254c78","tid":368410,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>You are lazy</blockquote><br />\nhow do you know?"},{"pid":"2ab7e53b570c346deba4ef8b1541c33475de294d","tid":368410,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e72dd543616296ec3ade65bea0e57bd7ab67759","tid":368410,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"}]}